    "localExecution": false,
    "description": "Create vault hosts from structured host objects. Use when the user wants to add/create a host (Vault → Hosts). NOT for Vault → Notes sidebar documentation. Use when the user wants to add/create a host in Vault → Hosts (创建主机、SSH 连接凭据). NOT for Vault → Notes sidebar docs. Put SSH password in password field; long remarks/admin tables in host notes field. Never fall back to vault_notes_create if this fails.",
